task.summary: OOP revision, start of new function adding
New function (djangonize templates) is complete (without comments)
Comments and documentation for DjangonizeTemplates is added
HTML RegEx correction (the program is able not only replace links on django-links, but replace non actual django-links on actual now)
The feature allows saving images in subfolders (for DjangoImage) is added
The feature allows log all files (images) in image folder and its subfolders is adding to the History class. Design of methods documentation is changed.
Exception and tooltip for "Import all" feature is corrected
currentImages (at History().import_all()) is refactored from list to list generator. Tooltip for "Import All" button is added. App info is corrected.
The table with django-links (Images history) can be refreshed internally now (without restart of the program). README update.
Django project for testing of djangonizeIt functions is added. Adding/correction of button tooltips in the app.
